                  form(action="/pledge",method="post")#bikes-form.well
                    h1 Bikers Registration Form
                    P Bike4Beds is a charitable event, and we ask everyone to raise money for the cause and/or invite additional riders. We don't require a set amount of fund raising, we only ask that riders do their best in helping with this cause.
                    P
                    P Please select a bike route and return transportation, you will find information about both of these choices on the "Upcoming Events" page.
                    P
                    div#block
                     label First Name
                     input(type="text", name="firstName", alt="First Name", id='firstName-tf', value='').span3.required
                    div#block1
                     label Last Name
                     input(type="text", name="lastName", alt="Last Name", id='lastName-tf', value='').span4.required
                    div#Street
                     label Street Address
                     input(type="text", name="streetAddr", alt="Street Addr", id='streetAddr-tf', value='').span7.required
                    div#blockCity
                      label City
                      input(type="text", name="city", alt="City", id='city-tf').span3.required
                    div#blockState
                      label State
                      select(type="text",name="state", alt="State", id='state-tf')#stateDw.span2.required
                    div#blockZip
                      label Zip
                      input(type="text", name="zip", alt="Zip", id='zip-tf')#zip.span2.required
                    div#blockEmail
                      label Email Address
                      input(type="text", name="email", alt="Email Address", id='email-tf').span4.required
                    div#blockPhoneNbr
                      label Phone Number
                      input(type="text", name="phoneNbr", alt="Phone Number", id='phoneNbr-tf')#phoneNbr.span3.required
                    div#Street
                      label Select an event to bike
                      select(type="text",name="bikeEvent", alt="Bike Event", id='bikeEvent-tf')#eventsDw.span5
                    div
                      label Select the bike route (please see upcoming events for more info)
                      select(type="text",name="bikeRoute", alt="Bike Route", id='bikeRoute-tf')#bikeRouteDw.span5
                    div
                      label Select transportation back to the start (please see upcoming events for more info)
                      select(type="text",name="transportation", alt="transportation", id='transportation-tf')#transportationDw.span5
                    div
                      label Shirt Size (technical shirt included in Bike Fee)
                      select(type="text",name="shirt", alt="Shirt Size", id='shirt-tf')#shirtDw.span4
                    div#Street
                    P
                    P The biking fee is $35 (includes technical shirt), along with the fee each biker is encouraged to get sponsorship by per mile or total.
                      select(type="text",name="sponsorship", alt="Sponsorship", id='sponsorship-tf')#sponsorshipDw.span5
                    div#Street
                    p
                    p Bike Waiver
                    p In consideration of the acceptance of this entry, I hereby for myself, my heirs, executors, administrator and assigns release and discharge Bike4Beds INC, their agents, and sponsors whose facilities, services and products are being used for this event, from any claims for damages suffered by me as a result of my participation in or traveling to or from said event. I specifically release and discharge the said promoters and sponsors and all participants, whose facilities are being used for this event, etc. from all injuries or damages arising from or contributed to any physical impairment or defect I may have, whether latent or patent, and agree that they are under no obligation to provide physical examination or other evidence of any fitness to participate in such event, the same being my responsibility. I also give permission for the free use of my name and picture in any broadcast, telecast or other written account of the event. I understand that helmets are required for riders under the age of 16 and recommended for riders 16 and over. I also understand that there will be regular traffic on these roads and I must adhere to all traffic laws and regulations.
                    div
                      input(type='checkbox',name="agreement",alt="Agreement", id='agreement-tf')#agreement.required
                      |   By checking this box, I agree with the above waiver.
                      p
                    div
                      input(type='checkbox',name='overSixteen', alt="Over Sixteen", id='overSixteen-tf')#over16.required
                      |   By checking this box, I agree I am over sixteen years of age.
                    div
                    p
                    p You must be over 18 years of age OR the parent/legal guardian of a minor under 18 years of age OR the legal guardian of an incapacitated and/or mentally challenged person in order to agree to the text above. Enter your Birth Date:
                    p
                      input(type="text", name="birthDate", alt="Birth Date", id='birthDate-tf')#birthDate.span2.required
